WEBVTT

00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:25.620
Teacher, teacher, good teacher, what must I do to inherit everlasting life?

00:00:25.620 --> 00:00:28.019
Why do you call me good?

00:00:28.019 --> 00:00:29.980
Nobody is good except one.

00:00:29.980 --> 00:00:38.240
God, you know the commandments.

00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:44.240
Do not murder, do not commit adultery, do not steal, do not bare false witness, do not

00:00:44.240 --> 00:00:47.119
defraud, honor your father and your mother.

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:56.140
All these things I have kept from my youth on.

00:00:56.140 --> 00:01:05.969
One thing is missing about you, go sell what things you have, and give to the poor, and

00:01:05.969 --> 00:01:21.290
you will have treasure in heaven, and come be my follower.

00:01:21.290 --> 00:01:30.599
But he grew sad at the answer, and went away grieved, for he had many possessions.
